documents.title: STARINN KYARI JUNGLE RESORT
documents.description: STARINN KYARI JUNGLE RESORT is a resort located in Village Kyari, Jim Corbett National Park, in the Nainital district of Uttarakhand, India. It is a unit of Star Inn Suites and Retreat Ltd.

company.name: Star Inn Suites and Retreat Ltd
company.services: The company provides holiday products and experiences through a network of resorts, hotels, and clubs in India and internationally.
company.packages: They offer various packages and have tie-ups with numerous resorts globally.
